title: Spaceman 10K Pro 5pk
description: Meet the SMOK Spaceman 10K Pro Disposable, the ultimate vape device that caters to both beginners and experts. This sleek and user-friendly vape offers a remarkable blend of convenience and performance, ensuring you enjoy every puff. With an incredible capacity of approximately 10,000 puffs, the Spaceman 10K Pro is designed to last. Its 16mL pre-filled tank means fewer refills and more uninterrupted vaping. The device also features a handy screen display window, making it easy to keep track of your settings, while the battery and e-liquid light indicators keep you informed about your device's status. Lightweight and portable, the Spaceman 10K Pro fits comfortably in your hand. It boasts draw-activation for seamless use and comes equipped with an 800mAh built-in vape battery that can be easily recharged via the USB Type-C port. Thanks to its anti-leak technology, you can say goodbye to messy leaks and enjoy a hassle-free vaping experience. Available in over 10 flavors, this device also offers two airflow control modes (MTL or RDL), allowing you to customize your vaping experience to your liking. Whether you prefer a tighter draw or a more relaxed one, the Spaceman 10K Pro has you covered.
